     h2.content-heading Who We Are
     p.about-content  Lynx is a clothing brand made just for women. We believe that every woman should feel strong, confident, and comfortable in what she wears. Our clothes are designed to match your lifestyle — whether you're working, relaxing, or going out.

     h2.content-heading  Our Mission
     p.about-content We want to help women feel good about themselves. That means offering clothes that are stylish, easy to wear, and made with care. We also care about the planet and choose materials that are better for the environment.

     h2.content-heading  Made for Women, by Women
     p.about-content Lynx is run by women who understand what other women need. We know that clothes should fit well, feel good, and make life easier — not harder. That’s why every piece we create is made with real women in mind.

     h2.content-heading  Join Us
     p.about-content Lynx isn’t just a brand — it’s a community. We’re here to help women feel their best, every single day. Come be a part of it.
     p.about-content “Lynx is about more than fashion. It’s about confidence, comfort, and feeling like yourself.”

     